python-vxfld (2.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * vxrd: improve responsiveness by adding netlink monitoring capability
  * vxsnd: now tracks addresses reported by vxrd
  * vxsnd: zeroes out UDP checksum in service node replication mode
  * google protocol buffers for serialization/deserialization
  * better code readability and much better documentation
  * many minor bug fixes

 -- Sameer Ladiwala <sameer@cumulusnetworks.com>  Fri, 04 Dec 2015 11:34:43 -0800

python-vxfld (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * vxsnd: ensure that the UDP checksum is always recalculated; Thanks markmcclain
  * vxrd: remove dstport check from device config validation; Thanks jordant
  * add license file to manifest.in for setup.py to work; Thanks drwahl
  * remove config files from setup; Thanks jordant

 -- Sameer Ladiwala <sameer@cumulusnetworks.com>  Fri, 04 Dec 2015 11:32:35 -0800

python-vxfld (2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * New maintainer
  * merged code from https://github.com/metacloud/vxfld
    - SND database sync at startup
    - ability to run as non-priveleged user
    - tiered replication/flooding
  * head end replication
  * eventlet for improved concurrency
  * pep8

 -- Sameer Ladiwala <sameer@cumulusnetworks.com>  Thu, 08 Oct 2015 18:26:10 -0700

